def productExceptSelf(nums):
    n = len(nums)
    answer = [1] * n
    
    # Left pass
    for i in range(1, n):
        answer[i] = answer[i-1] * nums[i-1]
    
    # Right pass
    right = 1
    for i in range(n-1, -1, -1):
        answer[i] *= right
        right *= nums[i]
    
    return answer
